{
  "title": "Robust Spicy Middle Eastern Lamb Maqluba",
  "description": "A spicy and flavorful Middle Eastern dish featuring lamb, brown rice, and spices, perfect for a hearty dinner. This low-calorie-friendly recipe is made with wholesome ingredients and is suitable for a weeknight meal.",
